            <p>Each method in the FRQ is worth 1 - 3 points. The method header is usually worth 1 point and the code in the method body is usually worth another point or two depending on how complex it is.</p>
            <p>This problem asks you to write a simple accessor method called <term>activeDays</term> which returns the number of active days (which should be an instance variable) for 1 point.</p>
